meta {
  name: List all default device posture checks
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/device-posture-checks/default
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Lists all default device posture checks. Default device posture checks are defined by Okta. Their type will always be `BUILTIN`.

**Responses:**
- `200`: OK
- `403`: 
- `429`:
}
